                          Ahora calculamos la segunda parte:
                          
                          $$
                          \int_{20}^{25}\frac{50-x}{750}\,dx
                        =
                          \frac{1}{750}\left[50x-\frac{x^2}{2}\right]_{20}^{25}
                        $$
                          
                          $$
                          =
                          \frac{1}{750}(937.5-800)
                        =
                          \frac{137.5}{750}
                        =
